column1: # This dataset provides a comprehensive look at Airbnb prices in London.

# The dataset includes information such as realSum (the total price of the listing); multi (indicator if the listing belongs to hosts with 2-4 offers); biz (indicator if the listing belongs to hosts with more than 4 offers); bedrooms (0 for studios); dist (distance from city center) ; attr_index (accessibility of attractions within the city); rest_index (accessibility of restaurants within the city) etc.
